\section*{Projects}
\subsection*{Fast-Track-Pizza (Restaurant Ordering System)}
\begin{itemize}[label=--]
\item Developed a frontend for a restaurant using React, React Redux, Redux Toolkit, and React Router.
\item Developed a responsive user interface with Tailwind CSS, ensuring optimal user experience on different devices.
\item Integrated API calls to load the restaurant menu dynamically, allowing users to view and select items.
\item Implemented a shopping cart functionality to enable users to order multiple pizzas and review their selections.
\item Added a feature for users to mark priority orders, with a 20\% additional charge, enhancing customer options.
\item Implemented testing with React Testing Library and Jest.
\end{itemize}

\subsection\*{Portfolio Website (Personal Showcase)}
\begin{itemize}[label=--]
\item Developed a personal portfolio website using React, React Icons, Email.js, Swiper, and TypeScript.
\item Created a dynamic and visually appealing showcase of projects, skills, and contact information.
\item Utilized React Icons for engaging visual elements and Swiper for smooth image carousels.
\item Integrated Email.js for a user-friendly contact form, allowing visitors to easily reach out.
\item Demonstrated proficiency in TypeScript for enhanced code quality and development experience.
\end{itemize}

\subsection\*{Customizable React UI Components Library}
\begin{itemize}[label=--]
\item Created a highly customizable React UI components library using React, Tailwind CSS, PropTypes, React Icons, and other technologies.
\item Implemented UI components including Custom-Navigation, Accordion, Button, Dropdown, Link, Modal, Panel, Route, Sidebar, and Sort-able Table.
\item Ensured modularity and re-usability of components, allowing easy integration across projects and facilitating collaboration within the team.
\item Promoted code quality by utilizing PropTypes and adhering to coding standards, contributing to a maintainable and scalable codebase.
\item Utilized Git and GitHub for version control and collaborative development.
\end{itemize}

\subsection\*{Natours Landing Page}
\begin{itemize}[label=--]
\item Developed a stunning landing page for a nature tour company using only HTML and SCSS.
\item Utilized a custom-built grid system with "BEM" class naming and 7-1 folder structure for organized and maintainable code.
\item Achieved full responsiveness with responsive images and ensured a beautiful and consistent user experience across various devices.
\item Implemented captivating animations for enhanced visual appeal and engagement.
\item Created a cards section with 180-degree hover animation, enhancing interactivity and user engagement.
\item Developed a hamburger navigation with open and close functionality for seamless navigation on small screens.
\item Created a beautiful modal for displaying additional information, enhancing user interaction and information accessibility.
\end{itemize}
